158
00:17:57,359 --> 00:17:59,680
[SPEAKER_00] On mi pet i šest kaže, mada evo ajmo te plakati.

159
00:18:00,400 --> 00:18:01,440
[SPEAKER_00] Pa vi Pa bit će vam dobro.

